Both servers are already running now — I restarted the backend a moment ago. Here's the current state:

| Server | Port | Status | How to restart if needed |
|--------|------|--------|-------------------------|
| **Frontend** (Next.js) | `:3000` | Running | `npx next dev -p 3000` |
