If you Ctrl+C either one again:
- **Frontend**: open a new terminal in the project root → `Start-Process -WindowStyle Hidden -FilePath "npx" -ArgumentList "next dev -p 3000"`
- **Backend**: open a new terminal in `backend/` → `Start-Process -WindowStyle Hidden -FilePath "npx" -ArgumentList "ts-node src/index.ts"`

Both are detached (hidden) processes so they survive terminal closes. If you want them visible in their own windows, drop the `-WindowStyle Hidden` flag.

